title: Kontakt 5 Expansions Vol. 1 (MaddLoadz)
description:
Kontakt Sound Expansions Vol. 1

Sound pack with amazing high quality sounds from multiple companies put together in one massive pack.

Chord Machine
EDM
Indiginus Guitars
Ivy Audio- Clare Solo
Ivy Audio- Piano in 162
Maybach Kings
Modern Guitars
Pure R&B
Rap Hooks
Sc Music Box
Speak & Spell
Supper Star O (4 VIP members only packs)

Urban Alien
Westcoast Riders Classic Edition


Also included:

Full unlocked version of Kontakt 5.4.2
How to instructions on how to remove old versions and install this one so sounds will work!

Stay tuned for more awesome high quality uploads by me MaddLoadz!!
